00:58:59,740 --> 00:59:03,580
It's okay if I make a fool of myself.
I can run back to Kyung Soo.

746
00:59:03,580 --> 00:59:09,170
I kept thinking about that and didn't
give up even though I was very nervous.

747
00:59:09,170 --> 00:59:13,160
Good job. I knew you would do a good job.

748
00:59:17,100 --> 00:59:19,000
Kyung Soo.

749
00:59:21,060 --> 00:59:27,920
