01:00:10,640 --> 01:00:12,700
why was Hae Dang's appearance canceled?

765
01:00:12,700 --> 01:00:17,080
- Right...
- You didn't even ask them why?

766
01:00:17,080 --> 01:00:20,400
And you want to work for
a management company?

767
01:00:20,400 --> 01:00:23,830
I looked into it. I talked
to the program crew

768
01:00:23,830 --> 01:00:28,130
and it turns out Yoo Ji Na asked

769
01:00:28,130 --> 01:00:31,240
that Jung Hae Dang
be removed from the program.

770
01:00:32,870 --> 01:00:36,340
- Why?
- The producers don't know either.

771
01:00:36,340 --> 01:00:39,580
She said that she would not
participate if Hae Dang was in.

772
01:00:39,580 --> 01:00:45,420
I believe the producers had no
choice but to listen to her request.

773
01:00:48,520 --> 01:00:50,310
I'm going to go change.

774
01:00:55,480 --> 01:00:58,580
Yoo Ji Na, that woman...

775
01:01:09,890 --> 01:01:14,010
She's not a stranger,
so I told her to wait inside.

776
01:01:16,280 --> 01:01:20,410
- Welcome.
- I will wait in the room next door.

777
01:01:20,410 --> 01:01:24,010
Change your clothes and let's talk.

778
01:01:40,170 --> 01:01:43,140
- Have a seat.
- Why...

779
01:01:43,140 --> 01:01:45,030
don't you want to participate with me?

780
01:01:45,030 --> 01:01:49,110
Are you already famous enough
to ask me such a question so boldly?

781
01:01:50,050 --> 01:01:51,940
After just signing a contract
with a company?

782
01:01:51,940 --> 01:01:56,460
I asked you why you don't
want to be participate with me.

783
01:01:56,460 --> 01:01:58,660
