787
01:02:06,920 --> 01:02:11,550
"Let's do our best
not to cross paths again."

788
01:02:12,980 --> 01:02:15,340
If you don't want to cross paths with me

789
01:02:15,340 --> 01:02:18,730
then you step back this time.

790
01:02:18,730 --> 01:02:24,630
I told you that I won't hold back
if you interfere in my life again!

791
01:02:24,630 --> 01:02:26,370
Are you done talking?

792
01:02:26,370 --> 01:02:31,230
Your TV appearance opportunity can
disappear at my request anytime.

793
01:02:31,230 --> 01:02:33,730
Do you know why?

794
01:02:33,730 --> 01:02:37,780
Because you impersonate me.

795
01:02:39,320 --> 01:02:42,320
Who's telling whom to step back?

796
01:02:42,320 --> 01:02:44,210
Weren't you the one who wanted to help me

797
01:02:44,210 --> 01:02:48,810
and tried to sign a contract with
the same company in the first place?

798
01:02:48,810 --> 01:02:51,360
All you have to do

799
01:02:51,360 --> 01:02:55,080
is take the help that I give you.

800
01:02:55,080 --> 01:02:57,640
Only the help I give you.

801
01:03:00,830 --> 01:03:04,090
I have another appointment
to go to, so...

802
01:03:04,090 --> 01:03:05,890
Did you...

803
01:03:07,450 --> 01:03:09,680
fall in love with someone again?

804
01:03:15,180 --> 01:03:20,600
Did you find something
that you want again?

805
01:03:20,600 --> 01:03:25,100
I guess that means that you will
do whatever it takes to get it.

806
01:03:27,110 --> 01:03:29,300
What are you trying to say?

807
01:03:29,300 --> 01:03:33,770
I'm trying to say that you
are someone who is willing

808
01:03:33,770 --> 01:03:41,620
to abandon your own child
to get the things you want.

809
01:03:41,620 --> 01:03:43,370
Yoo Ji Na.

